‘bmkp-edit-annotation’             ‘a e’       Edit this line's
                                               annotation.
‘bmkp-show-all-annotations’        ‘a A’       Show all annotations.
‘bmkp-bmenu-edit-annotations-for-marked’‘a >’  Edit annotations for
                                               marked.
‘bmkp-bmenu-show-this-annotation+move-down’‘M-<down>’Move + show.
‘bmkp-bmenu-show-this-annotation+move-up’‘M-<up>’Same, going up.

   Annotated bookmarks are flagged with ‘a’ in the display.


