12 Highlighting Bookmark Locations
**********************************

Optional--requires ‘bookmark+-lit.el’ on your ‘load-path’.  Bookmark+
can draw a persistent “highlight” at the position (or region, or line,
or fringe) of a bookmark in its buffer.

