‘non-autonamed-bookmark’, ‘any-bookmark’, ‘autonamed-in-buffer’,
‘non-autonamed-in-buffer’, ‘all-in-buffer’, ‘nil’ (off).

12.4 Pulse Highlight on Jump
============================

If ‘bmkp-highlight-on-jump-flag’ is non-nil (the default), jumping to a
bookmark that has no region briefly pulse-highlights the landing line
via the built-in ‘pulse.el’.


