18 Temporary Bookmarks
**********************

A “temporary” bookmark is one that will not be written to the bookmark
file.  It exists only for the current session.

18.1 Temporary-Bookmarking Mode
===============================

‘bmkp-temporary-bookmarking-mode’ (‘M-L’ in ‘*Bmkp List*’) turns on a
minor mode that:

  1. Switches to an empty bookmark file.
  2. Turns off auto-saving (‘bookmark-save-flag’).

   Every bookmark you create in this mode is therefore session-local.
The mode-line indicator changes to ‘TEMPORARY Bookmarking’.

