18.3 Autotemp Predicates
========================

‘bmkp-autotemp-bookmark-predicates’ is a list of predicates-- typically
type predicates such as ‘bmkp-autonamed-bookmark-p’-- that decide which
bookmarks become temporary automatically when created or updated.  The
default makes autonamed bookmarks temporary.

   ‘bmkp-delete-all-temporary-bookmarks’ removes them all from the
current list at once.

   Temporary bookmarks are flagged with ‘X’ in ‘*Bmkp List*’.


